### 3.3 Risk Screening

The following triggers require escalation to {{ ai_governance_contact if ai_governance_contact else "the AI governance contact" }} before proceeding:

| Risk Indicator | Impact |
|----------------|--------|
| Processes personal information | Triggers APP compliance review |
| Processes sensitive information | Requires PIA |
| Makes automated decisions affecting individuals | Triggers POLA Act assessment |
| Sends data overseas | Triggers APP 8 cross-border assessment |
| Free-tier or unclear data handling terms | Requires enhanced vendor due diligence |
| Processes data of children under 18 | Requires escalation to senior leadership |
| Is customer-facing | Requires transparency and disclosure review |

{% if "Health Information" in data_types_processed %}- The tool will process **health information** — requires escalation regardless of classification tier{% endif %}

