## 5. Approval Process

### 5.1 Approval Tiers

| Data Classification | Risk Level | Approver | Additional Requirements |
|--------------------|------------|----------|------------------------|
| Public | Low | Team manager | Standard evaluation |
| Internal | Low | Team manager + IT review | Standard evaluation + security check |
| Confidential | Medium | {{ ai_governance_contact if ai_governance_contact else "AI governance contact" }} | Full evaluation + DPA signed |
| Confidential | High | {{ ai_governance_contact if ai_governance_contact else "AI governance contact" }} + senior leadership | Full evaluation + DPA + PIA |
| Restricted | Any | Senior leadership + legal | Full evaluation + DPA + PIA + legal review |
| Automated decisions | Any | Senior leadership | Full evaluation + PIA + POLA Act assessment |

