### 5.2 Privacy Impact Assessment

A PIA is **required** when the AI tool:
- Processes sensitive information (health, biometric, children's data)
- Makes automated decisions affecting individuals
- Introduces a new type of personal information collection
- Processes data overseas for the first time

{% if pia_conducted %}
{{ business_name }} has experience conducting PIAs. Apply the same methodology to new AI tools.
{% else %}
{{ business_name }} has not yet conducted a PIA. The OAIC provides PIA guidance at [www.oaic.gov.au](https://www.oaic.gov.au). Consider engaging external privacy counsel for the first PIA.
{% endif %}

