## 6. Trial and Sandbox Requirements

All new AI tools must undergo a **mandatory trial period** before full production deployment:

| Requirement | Detail |
|-------------|--------|
| Trial duration | Minimum 30 days, maximum 90 days |
| Data restriction | Trial must use **Public or Internal data only** — no Confidential or Restricted data |
| User restriction | Maximum 5 users during trial unless otherwise approved |
| Monitoring | Weekly usage and output reviews during trial |
| Success criteria | Defined before trial begins — must be measurable |
| Trial exit decision | Approve for production, extend trial, or decommission |

{% if ai_generated_content_reviewed %}
{{ business_name }} reviews AI-generated content before use. During trial periods, **all** AI outputs must be reviewed by a designated reviewer before being used in any business process.
{% else %}
**Recommendation:** {{ business_name }} should implement AI output review processes, particularly during trial periods, to assess accuracy and suitability before production rollout.
{% endif %}

